msgstr "Kanban"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:51
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Event Tracks` page opens in the :icon:`oi-view-"
"kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` view, providing users an at-a-glance overview "
"of all tracks for the selected event."
msgstr ""
"โดยค่าเริ่มต้น หน้า:guilabel:`แทร็กอีเวนต์`จะเปิดในมุมมอง:icon:`oi-view-kanban` "
":guilabel:`(Kanban)`ซึ่งให้ภาพรวมอย่างรวดเร็วของแทร็กทั้งหมดสำหรับอีเวนต์ที่เลือก"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:0
msgid "Typical event tracks page for an event in the Odoo Events application."
msgstr "หน้าแทร็กอีเวนต์ทั่วไปสำหรับอีเวนต์ในแอปพลิเคชัน Odoo อีเวนต์"

#: ../../content/applications/marketing/events/attendee_experience/event_tracks.rst:58
msgid ""
"In the default :icon:`oi-view-kanban` :guilabel:`(Kanban)` view, the tracks "
"are categorized into several modifiable "
"stages: :guilabel:`Proposal` :guilabel:`Confirmed`, :guilabel:`Announced`, :guilabel:`Published`, :guilabel:`Refused` "
